        {
            "title": "鮑威爾明言關稅及影響比預期大  惟調整政策為時過早 需了解更多細節",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"鮑威爾明言關稅及影響比預期大  惟調整政策為時過早 需了解更多細節\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4c1b5285251b9b80639bac99f32f45f3/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040509220873171.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">鮑威爾明言關稅及影響比預期大  惟調整政策為時過早 需了解更多細節</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>聯儲局主席鮑威爾在周五（4日）發表講話時表示，目前經濟面對高度不確定的前景，存在更高失業和更高通脹的風險，並明確指評估提高關稅對經濟可能帶來的影響是非常困難，直至有更多關於關稅細節的訊息，如關稅對象、稅率和持續時間，以及貿易夥伴的報復措施。不過，他指現在顯然可以預見關稅提高幅度比預期大，經濟影響也比預期更顯著，包括更高通脹和較慢增長。\n\n</p><h2>數據表明經濟增長仍穩健</h2>\n<p>鮑威爾又重申，聯儲局專注於兩大使命，即最大化就業和穩定物價；儘管不確定性很高，但經濟仍處於良好狀態，最新數據亦表明經濟增長穩健，勞動力市場保持平衡，通脹率接近但仍高於2%目標。\n\n</p><h2>評論政府政策非儲局職責</h2>\n<p>他提到，新一屆政府正在實施4個不同領域的重大政策變化，包括貿易、移民、財政政策和監管，而聯儲局的貨幣政策立場已為應對這些風險和不確定性做好了準備，並將在對政策變化及其可能影響有更清晰理解後作出調整，但評論這些政策並非聯儲局的職責。\n\n</p>\n<p>此外，聯儲局將繼續仔細監察即將發佈的數據、經濟前景變化及風險的平衡，並指對經濟未來前景有更明確認識之前，政策立場不會輕易調整，現在下結論說貨幣政策的適當路徑還為時過早。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062208/即時-財經-鮑威爾明言關稅及影響比預期大-惟調整政策為時過早-需了解更多細節",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-05 09:31:40",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "愛民邨鬍鬚男吸煙惹食客不滿 遭2漢雨傘扑爆鼻 3人混戰被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"愛民邨鬍鬚男吸煙惹食客不滿 遭2漢雨傘扑爆鼻 3人混戰被捕\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e5de8724be69e03edd199794e140384d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040509173366045.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">愛民邨鬍鬚男吸煙惹食客不滿 遭2漢雨傘扑爆鼻 3人混戰被捕</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今(5日)早上7時22分，一名男子報案指在何文田愛民邨遭2至3人用雨傘襲擊，並搶去他的手機，行兇者仍在現場附近，警員接報趕至，經調查後，以公眾地方打架罪名拘捕3名涉案男子。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177812/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/397085f221387aec2e8ca7b32177db36/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_084612427_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177813/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/99f3cb8f97f7fe185f697f44975fb641/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_084612427_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177814/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/821c222395856ac8f610fa22454c07fd/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_084612427_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177815/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"事發餐廳。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76e816e91f7b86d3e3e15736e0993580/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_084612427_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        事發餐廳。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177816/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"事發冬菇亭餐廳。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/77564afbe75ffba76a836792413833f8/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_084612427_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        事發冬菇亭餐廳。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177817/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"吸煙男受傷送院。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e0b08a28a903bb68bd7ad668c429b7b4/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_084800482_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        吸煙男受傷送院。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177818/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"兩名食客涉公眾地方打架被捕。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/85b86be0ac60d3ad18480213abaa1b29/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_084800482_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩名食客涉公眾地方打架被捕。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177819/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"吸煙男受傷送院。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/07cb17782eb522d3ccae1deeb5b97c64/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_084921822_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        吸煙男受傷送院。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177820/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場遺下遭扔在馬路的手機。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0ca7df073367eb717c47fb010df0c093/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_085417323.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場遺下遭扔在馬路的手機。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>現場為愛民邨冬姑亭一餐廳，一名中年漢在餐廳後門附近吸煙，煙味影響其中一枱兩名男食客，兩人與吸煙男初則口角，兩食客用雨傘扑傷吸煙男，再忿然搶去吸煙男的手機擲到對面馬路，其他乘客見狀報警求助。警方到場經調查後拘捕3名男子，其中吸煙男鼻部受傷送院治理。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062207/即時-港聞-愛民邨鬍鬚男吸煙惹食客不滿-遭2漢雨傘扑爆鼻-3人混戰被捕",
